AB  - The panel symposium delves into the evolving landscape of entrepreneurial finance, addressing current challenges, market frictions, and explores innovative methodologies to research these challenges. Bringing together esteemed scholars, the session highlights new trends in research on venture capital, crowdfunding, and alternative funding mechanisms, with a particular focus on demographic biases. Methodologically, the symposium focusses on the use of experimental approaches and new technologies to uncover biases and validate theoretical frameworks.
